import json
with open('baseline-packages.json') as f: b = json.load(f)
with open('after-cpm-packages.json') as f: a = json.load(f)
# Compare per project
for bp, ap in zip(b['projects'], a['projects']):
    name = bp['path'].split('/')[-2]
    for bf, af in zip(bp['frameworks'], ap['frameworks']):
        bpkgs = {p['id']: p['resolvedVersion'] for p in bf.get('topLevelPackages',[])}
        apkgs = {p['id']: p['resolvedVersion'] for p in af.get('topLevelPackages',[])}
        if bpkgs != apkgs:
            print(f'DIFF in {name}/{bf[\"framework\"]}: baseline={bpkgs} after={apkgs}')
print('Package comparison: all versions match baseline.')
"

